<br>
Jewelcraft is one of the most expensive tradeskills there is.  Typically, no one person can get to 250 skill by themselves.  Most guilds have a designated jeweler, and they help fund that jeweler to practice their skill.  The person who suffers the loss most, in the end, usually is still that jeweler.<br>
<br>
